1. Uznemirena sam ovom vesti koju sam čula. (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (I am disturbed by this news that I heard.)

2. Ona je uznemirena zbog zdravstvenih problema svog oca. (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (She is disturbed by her father's health problems.)

3. Uznemirena sam kada vidim nasilje na televiziji. (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (I am disturbed when I see violence on television.)

4. Uznemirena sam, jer mi se još niko nije javio. (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (I am upset because no one has contacted me yet.)

5. Ona je bila uznemirena kada je videla svog psa da beži sa dvorišta. (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (She was upset when she saw her dog running away from the yard.)

6. Da li ste primetili koliko je uznemirena ova situacija? (*uznemirena* - adjective, feminine singular) (Have you noticed how disturbing this situation is?)

7. Kada sam čula da je moja najbolja prijateljica otišla u bolnicu, osećala sam se uznemireno. (*uznemireno* - adjective, neuter singular) (When I heard that my best friend went to the hospital, I felt disturbed.)

8. Moje uznemireno srce je počelo da kuca sve brže i brže. (*uznemireno* - adjective, neuter singular) (My disturbed heart began to beat faster and faster.)

9. Uznemireno sam odlučila da napustim tu zabavu. (*uznemireno* - adverb) (Disturbed, I decided to leave that party.)

10. Njeno uznemireno ponašanje je upozorilo druge da se ne približavaju. (*uznemireno* - adjective, neuter singular) (Her disturbed behavior warned others not to approach.)